snippet: Field Marshal Mohamed Hussein Tantawi said that the military would not offer a candidate to be Egypt’s next president.
lead_paragraph: Field Marshal Mohamed Hussein Tantawi said that the military would not offer a candidate to be Egypt’s next president.
